Maintainer: Jeffry Hesse <jhesse@sonatype.com>
Description: Collects a list of your third party R packages, and
    scans them with 'Sonatype's OSS Index', reporting back on any
    vulnerabilities that are found in the third party packages you use.
License: Apache License 2.0 | file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/sonatype-nexus-community/oysteR
